5865 void Player::LoadCorpse(PreparedQueryResult result)
5866 {
5867  if (IsAlive() || HasAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_RESURRECT))
5868  SpawnCorpseBones(false);
5869 
5870  if (!IsAlive())
5871  {
5872  if (result && !HasAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_RESURRECT))
5873  {
5874  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
5875  _corpseLocation.WorldRelocate(fields[0].GetUInt16(), fields[1].GetFloat(), fields[2].GetFloat(), fields[3].GetFloat(), fields[4].GetFloat());
5876  ApplyModFlag(PLAYER_FIELD_BYTES, PLAYER_FIELD_BYTE_RELEASE_TIMER, !sMapStore.LookupEntry(_corpseLocation.GetMapId())->Instanceable());
5877  }
5878  else
5879  ResurrectPlayer(0.5f);
5880  }
5881 
5882  RemoveAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_RESURRECT);
5883 }
5884 
5885 void Player::_LoadInventory(PreparedQueryResult result, uint32 timeDiff)
5886 {
5887  //QueryResult* result = CharacterDatabase.PQuery("SELECT data, text, bag, slot, item, item_template FROM character_inventory JOIN item_instance ON character_inventory.item = item_instance.guid WHERE character_inventory.guid = '%u' ORDER BY bag, slot", GetGUID().GetCounter());
5888  //NOTE: the "order by `bag`" is important because it makes sure
5889  //the bagMap is filled before items in the bags are loaded
5890  //NOTE2: the "order by `slot`" is needed because mainhand weapons are (wrongly?)
5891  //expected to be equipped before offhand items (TODO: fixme)
5892 
5893  if (result)
5894  {
5895  uint32 zoneId = GetZoneId();
5896 
5897  std::map<ObjectGuid::LowType, Bag*> bagMap; // fast guid lookup for bags
5898  std::map<ObjectGuid::LowType, Item*> invalidBagMap; // fast guid lookup for bags
5899  std::list<Item*> problematicItems;
5900  CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans = CharacterDatabase.BeginTransaction();
5901 
5902  // Prevent items from being added to the queue while loading
5903  m_itemUpdateQueueBlocked = true;
5904  do
5905  {
5906  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
5907  if (Item* item = _LoadItem(trans, zoneId, timeDiff, fields))
5908  {
5909  ObjectGuid::LowType bagGuid = fields[11].GetUInt32();
5910  uint8 slot = fields[12].GetUInt8();
5911 
5912  uint8 err = EQUIP_ERR_OK;
5913  // Item is not in bag
5914  if (!bagGuid)
5915  {
5916  item->SetContainer(nullptr);
5917  item->SetSlot(slot);
5918 
5919  if (IsInventoryPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot))
5920  {
5921  ItemPosCountVec dest;
5922  err = CanStoreItem(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot, dest, item, false);
5923  if (err == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5924  item = StoreItem(dest, item, true);
5925  }
5926  else if (IsEquipmentPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot))
5927  {
5928  uint16 dest;
5929  if (sScriptMgr->CheckItemInSlotAtLoadInventory(this, item, slot, err, dest))
5930  err = CanEquipItem(slot, dest, item, false, false);
5931  if (err == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5932  QuickEquipItem(dest, item);
5933  }
5934  else if (IsBankPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot))
5935  {
5936  ItemPosCountVec dest;
5937  err = CanBankItem(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, slot, dest, item, false, false);
5938  if (err == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5939  item = BankItem(dest, item, true);
5940  }
5941 
5942  // Remember bags that may contain items in them
5943  if (err == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5944  {
5945  if (IsBagPos(item->GetPos()))
5946  if (Bag* pBag = item->ToBag())
5947  bagMap[item->GetGUID().GetCounter()] = pBag;
5948  }
5949  else if (IsBagPos(item->GetPos()))
5950  if (item->IsBag())
5951  invalidBagMap[item->GetGUID().GetCounter()] = item;
5952  }
5953  else
5954  {
5955  item->SetSlot(NULL_SLOT);
5956  // Item is in the bag, find the bag
5957  std::map<ObjectGuid::LowType, Bag*>::iterator itr = bagMap.find(bagGuid);
5958  if (itr != bagMap.end())
5959  {
5960  ItemPosCountVec dest;
5961  err = CanStoreItem(itr->second->GetSlot(), slot, dest, item);
5962  if (err == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5963  item = StoreItem(dest, item, true);
5964  }
5965  else if (invalidBagMap.find(bagGuid) != invalidBagMap.end())
5966  {
5967  std::map<ObjectGuid::LowType, Item*>::iterator iterator = invalidBagMap.find(bagGuid);
5968  if (std::find(problematicItems.begin(), problematicItems.end(), iterator->second) != problematicItems.end())
5969  {
5970  err = EQUIP_ERR_INT_BAG_ERROR;
5971  }
5972  }
5973  else
5974  {
5975  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has item (%s, entry: %u) which doesnt have a valid bag (Bag GUID: %u, slot: %u). Possible cheat?",
5976  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry(), bagGuid, slot);
5977  item->DeleteFromInventoryDB(trans);
5978  delete item;
5979  continue;
5980  }
5981  }
5982 
5983  // Item's state may have changed after storing
5984  if (err == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
5985  item->SetState(ITEM_UNCHANGED, this);
5986  else
5987  {
5988  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has item (%s, entry: %u) which can't be loaded into inventory (Bag GUID: %u, slot: %u) by reason %u. Item will be sent by mail.",
5989  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry(), bagGuid, slot, err);
5990  item->DeleteFromInventoryDB(trans);
5991  problematicItems.push_back(item);
5992  }
5993  }
5994  } while (result->NextRow());
5995 
5996  m_itemUpdateQueueBlocked = false;
5997 
5998  // Send problematic items by mail
5999  while (!problematicItems.empty())
6000  {
6001  std::string subject = GetSession()->GetAcoreString(LANG_NOT_EQUIPPED_ITEM);
6002 
6003  MailDraft draft(subject, "There were problems with equipping item(s).");
6004  for (uint8 i = 0; !problematicItems.empty() && i < MAX_MAIL_ITEMS; ++i)
6005  {
6006  draft.AddItem(problematicItems.front());
6007  problematicItems.pop_front();
6008  }
6009  draft.SendMailTo(trans, this, MailSender(this, MAIL_STATIONERY_GM), MAIL_CHECK_MASK_COPIED);
6010  }
6011  CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
6012  }
6013  //if (IsAlive())
6014  _ApplyAllItemMods();
6015 }
6016 
6017 Item* Player::_LoadItem(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans, uint32 zoneId, uint32 timeDiff, Field* fields)
6018 {
6019  Item* item = nullptr;
6020  ObjectGuid::LowType itemGuid = fields[13].GetUInt32();
6021  uint32 itemEntry = fields[14].GetUInt32();
6022  if (ItemTemplate const* proto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(itemEntry))
6023  {
6024  bool remove = false;
6025  item = NewItemOrBag(proto);
6026  if (item->LoadFromDB(itemGuid, GetGUID(), fields, itemEntry))
6027  {
6028  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
6029 
6030  // Do not allow to have item limited to another map/zone in alive state
6031  if (IsAlive() && item->IsLimitedToAnotherMapOrZone(GetMapId(), zoneId))
6032  {
6033  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s', map: %u) has item (%s, entry: %u) limited to another map (%u). Deleting item.",
6034  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), GetMapId(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry(), zoneId);
6035  remove = true;
6036  }
6037  // "Conjured items disappear if you are logged out for more than 15 minutes"
6038  else if (timeDiff > 15 * MINUTE && proto->Flags & ITEM_FLAG_CONJURED)
6039  {
6040  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s', diff: %u) has conjured item (%s, entry: %u) with expired lifetime (15 minutes). Deleting item.",
6041  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), timeDiff, item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry());
6042  remove = true;
6043  }
6044  else if (item->HasFlag(ITEM_FIELD_FLAGS, ITEM_FIELD_FLAG_REFUNDABLE))
6045  {
6046  if (item->GetPlayedTime() > (2 * HOUR))
6047  {
6048  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has item (%s, entry: %u) with expired refund time (%u). Deleting refund data and removing refundable flag.",
6049  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry(), item->GetPlayedTime());
6050  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_ITEM_REFUND_INSTANCE);
6051  stmt->setUInt32(0, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
6052  trans->Append(stmt);
6053 
6054  item->RemoveFlag(ITEM_FIELD_FLAGS, ITEM_FIELD_FLAG_REFUNDABLE);
6055  }
6056  else
6057  {
6058  // xinef: zomg! sync query
6059  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_ITEM_REFUNDS);
6060  stmt->setUInt32(0, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
6061  stmt->setUInt32(1, GetGUID().GetCounter());
6062  if (PreparedQueryResult result = CharacterDatabase.Query(stmt))
6063  {
6064  item->SetRefundRecipient((*result)[0].GetUInt32());
6065  item->SetPaidMoney((*result)[1].GetUInt32());
6066  item->SetPaidExtendedCost((*result)[2].GetUInt16());
6067  AddRefundReference(item->GetGUID());
6068  }
6069  else
6070  {
6071  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has item (%s, entry: %u) with refundable flags, but without data in item_refund_instance. Removing flag.",
6072  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry());
6073  item->RemoveFlag(ITEM_FIELD_FLAGS, ITEM_FIELD_FLAG_REFUNDABLE);
6074  }
6075  }
6076  }
6077  else if (item->HasFlag(ITEM_FIELD_FLAGS, ITEM_FIELD_FLAG_BOP_TRADEABLE))
6078  {
6079  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_ITEM_BOP_TRADE);
6080  stmt->setUInt32(0, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
6081  if (PreparedQueryResult result = CharacterDatabase.Query(stmt))
6082  {
6083  std::string strGUID = (*result)[0].GetString();
6084  Tokenizer GUIDlist(strGUID, ' ');
6085  AllowedLooterSet looters;
6086  for (Tokenizer::const_iterator itr = GUIDlist.begin(); itr != GUIDlist.end(); ++itr)
6087  looters.insert(ObjectGuid::Create<HighGuid::Player>(atol(*itr)));
6088 
6089  if (looters.size() > 1 && item->GetTemplate()->GetMaxStackSize() == 1 && item->IsSoulBound())
6090  {
6091  item->SetSoulboundTradeable(looters);
6092  AddTradeableItem(item);
6093  }
6094  else
6095  item->ClearSoulboundTradeable(this);
6096  }
6097  else
6098  {
6099  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has item (%s, entry: %u) with ITEM_FIELD_FLAG_BOP_TRADEABLE flag, but without data in item_soulbound_trade_data. Removing flag.",
6100  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), item->GetEntry());
6101  item->RemoveFlag(ITEM_FIELD_FLAGS, ITEM_FIELD_FLAG_BOP_TRADEABLE);
6102  }
6103  }
6104  else if (proto->HolidayId)
6105  {
6106  remove = true;
6107  GameEventMgr::GameEventDataMap const& events = sGameEventMgr->GetEventMap();
6108  GameEventMgr::ActiveEvents const& activeEventsList = sGameEventMgr->GetActiveEventList();
6109  for (GameEventMgr::ActiveEvents::const_iterator itr = activeEventsList.begin(); itr != activeEventsList.end(); ++itr)
6110  {
6111  if (uint32(events[*itr].holiday_id) == proto->HolidayId)
6112  {
6113  remove = false;
6114  break;
6115  }
6116  }
6117  }
6118  }
6119  else
6120  {
6121  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has broken item (GUID: %u, entry: %u) in inventory. Deleting item.",
6122  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), itemGuid, itemEntry);
6123  remove = true;
6124  }
6125  // Remove item from inventory if necessary
6126  if (remove)
6127  {
6128  Item::DeleteFromInventoryDB(trans, itemGuid);
6129  item->FSetState(ITEM_REMOVED);
6130  item->SaveToDB(trans); // it also deletes item object!
6131  item = nullptr;
6132  }
6133  }
6134  else
6135  {
6136  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player::_LoadInventory: player (%s, name: '%s') has unknown item (entry: %u) in inventory. Deleting item.",
6137  GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetName().c_str(), itemEntry);
6138  Item::DeleteFromInventoryDB(trans, itemGuid);
6139  Item::DeleteFromDB(trans, itemGuid);
6140  }
6141  return item;
6142 }
6143 
6144 // load mailed item which should receive current player
6145 Item* Player::_LoadMailedItem(ObjectGuid const& playerGuid, Player* player, uint32 mailId, Mail* mail, Field* fields)
6146 {
6147  ObjectGuid::LowType itemGuid = fields[11].GetUInt32();
6148  uint32 itemEntry = fields[12].GetUInt32();
6149 
6150  ItemTemplate const* proto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(itemEntry);
6151  if (!proto)
6152  {
6153  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player %s (%s) has unknown item in mailed items (GUID: %u, Entry: %u) in mail (%u), deleted.",
6154  player ? player->GetName().c_str() : "<unknown>", playerGuid.ToString().c_str(), itemGuid, itemEntry, mailId);
6155 
6156  CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans = CharacterDatabase.BeginTransaction();
6157 
6158  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_INVALID_MAIL_ITEM);
6159  stmt->setUInt32(0, itemGuid);
6160  trans->Append(stmt);
6161 
6162  CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
6163  return nullptr;
6164  }
6165 
6166  Item* item = NewItemOrBag(proto);
6167 
6168  ObjectGuid ownerGuid = fields[13].GetUInt32() ? ObjectGuid::Create<HighGuid::Player>(fields[13].GetUInt32()) : ObjectGuid::Empty;
6169  if (!item->LoadFromDB(itemGuid, ownerGuid, fields, itemEntry))
6170  {
6171  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player::_LoadMailedItems: Item (GUID: %u) in mail (%u) doesn't exist, deleted from mail.", itemGuid, mailId);
6172 
6173  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_MAIL_ITEM);
6174  stmt->setUInt32(0, itemGuid);
6175  CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
6176 
6177  item->FSetState(ITEM_REMOVED);
6178 
6179  CharacterDatabaseTransaction temp = CharacterDatabaseTransaction(nullptr);
6180  item->SaveToDB(temp);
6181  return nullptr;
6182  }
6183 
6184  if (mail)
6185  {
6186  mail->AddItem(itemGuid, itemEntry);
6187  }
6188 
6189  if (player)
6190  {
6191  player->AddMItem(item);
6192  }
6193 
6194  return item;
6195 }
6196 
6197 void Player::_LoadMail(PreparedQueryResult mailsResult, PreparedQueryResult mailItemsResult)
6198 {
6199  std::set<uint32> pendingAuctions;
6200  std::unordered_map<uint32, Mail*> pendingAuctionMails;
6201  CharacterDatabaseTransaction pendingAuctionsTrans = CharacterDatabase.BeginTransaction();
6202 
6203  m_mail.clear();
6204 
6205  std::unordered_map<uint32, Mail*> mailById;
6206 
6207  if (mailsResult)
6208  {
6209  do
6210  {
6211  Field* fields = mailsResult->Fetch();
6212  Mail* m = new Mail;
6213 
6214  m->messageID = fields[0].GetUInt32();
6215  m->messageType = fields[1].GetUInt8();
6216  m->sender = fields[2].GetUInt32();
6217  m->receiver = fields[3].GetUInt32();
6218  m->subject = fields[4].GetString();
6219  m->body = fields[5].GetString();
6220  m->expire_time = time_t(fields[6].GetUInt32());
6221  m->deliver_time = time_t(fields[7].GetUInt32());
6222  m->money = fields[8].GetUInt32();
6223  m->COD = fields[9].GetUInt32();
6224  m->checked = fields[10].GetUInt8();
6225  m->stationery = fields[11].GetUInt8();
6226  m->mailTemplateId = fields[12].GetInt16();
6227  m->auctionId = fields[13].GetInt32();
6228 
6229  if (m->mailTemplateId && !sMailTemplateStore.LookupEntry(m->mailTemplateId))
6230  {
6231  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player::_LoadMail: Mail (%u) has nonexistent MailTemplateId (%u), remove at load", m->messageID, m->mailTemplateId);
6232  m->mailTemplateId = 0;
6233  }
6234 
6235  m->state = MAIL_STATE_UNCHANGED;
6236 
6237  // Do not load expired pending sale mail if there is already delivery auction mail
6238  if (m->auctionId < 0 && m->expire_time <= time(nullptr))
6239  {
6240  uint32 auctionId = std::abs(m->auctionId);
6241  if (pendingAuctions.count(auctionId))
6242  {
6243  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt2 = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_MAIL_BY_ID);
6244  stmt2->setUInt32(0, m->messageID);
6245  pendingAuctionsTrans->Append(stmt2);
6246 
6247  if (unReadMails > 0 && (m->checked & MAIL_CHECK_MASK_READ) == 0)
6248  --unReadMails;
6249 
6250  delete m;
6251  continue;
6252  }
6253 
6254  pendingAuctionMails[auctionId] = m;
6255  }
6256  else if (m->auctionId > 0)
6257  {
6258  pendingAuctions.insert(m->auctionId);
6259  }
6260 
6261  for (auto itr : pendingAuctionMails)
6262  {
6263  uint32 auctionId = itr.first;
6264  if (pendingAuctions.count(auctionId))
6265  {
6266  Mail* mail = itr.second;
6267 
6268  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt2 = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_MAIL_BY_ID);
6269  stmt2->setUInt32(0, mail->messageID);
6270  pendingAuctionsTrans->Append(stmt2);
6271 
6272  if (unReadMails > 0 && (mail->checked & MAIL_CHECK_MASK_READ) == 0)
6273  {
6274  --unReadMails;
6275  }
6276 
6277  m_mail.erase(std::remove(m_mail.begin(), m_mail.end(), mail));
6278 
6279  delete mail;
6280  }
6281  }
6282 
6283  m_mail.push_back(m);
6284  mailById[m->messageID] = m;
6285  } while (mailsResult->NextRow());
6286  }
6287 
6288  if (mailItemsResult)
6289  {
6290  do
6291  {
6292  Field* fields = mailItemsResult->Fetch();
6293  uint32 mailId = fields[14].GetUInt32();
6294  _LoadMailedItem(GetGUID(), this, mailId, mailById[mailId], fields);
6295  } while (mailItemsResult->NextRow());
6296  }
6297 
6298  CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(pendingAuctionsTrans);
6299  UpdateNextMailTimeAndUnreads();
6300 }

6312 void Player::_LoadQuestStatus(PreparedQueryResult result)
6313 {
6314  uint16 slot = 0;
6315 
6317  //QueryResult* result = CharacterDatabase.PQuery("SELECT quest, status, explored, timer, mobcount1, mobcount2, mobcount3, mobcount4, itemcount1, itemcount2, itemcount3,
6318  // 11 12 13 14
6319  // itemcount4, itemcount5, itemcount6, playercount FROM character_queststatus WHERE guid = '%u'", GetGUID().GetCounter());
6320 
6321  if (result)
6322  {
6323  do
6324  {
6325  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
6326 
6327  uint32 quest_id = fields[0].GetUInt32();
6328  // used to be new, no delete?
6329  Quest const* quest = sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(quest_id);
6330  if (quest)
6331  {
6332  // find or create
6333  QuestStatusData& questStatusData = m_QuestStatus[quest_id];
6334 
6335  uint8 qstatus = fields[1].GetUInt8();
6336  if (qstatus < MAX_QUEST_STATUS)
6337  questStatusData.Status = QuestStatus(qstatus);
6338  else
6339  {
6340  questStatusData.Status = QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE;
6341  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player %s (%s) has invalid quest %d status (%u), replaced by QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE(3).",
6342  GetName().c_str(), GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), quest_id, qstatus);
6343  }
6344 
6345  questStatusData.Explored = (fields[2].GetUInt8() > 0);
6346 
6347  time_t quest_time = time_t(fields[3].GetUInt32());
6348 
6349  if (quest->HasSpecialFlag(QUEST_SPECIAL_FLAGS_TIMED) && !GetQuestRewardStatus(quest_id))
6350  {
6351  AddTimedQuest(quest_id);
6352 
6353  if (quest_time <= sWorld->GetGameTime())
6354  questStatusData.Timer = 1;
6355  else
6356  questStatusData.Timer = uint32((quest_time - sWorld->GetGameTime()) * IN_MILLISECONDS);
6357  }
6358  else
6359  quest_time = 0;
6360 
6361  for (uint32 i = 0; i < QUEST_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; ++i)
6362  questStatusData.CreatureOrGOCount[i] = fields[4 + i].GetUInt16();
6363 
6364  for (uint32 i = 0; i < QUEST_ITEM_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; ++i)
6365  questStatusData.ItemCount[i] = fields[8 + i].GetUInt16();
6366 
6367  questStatusData.PlayerCount = fields[14].GetUInt16();
6368 
6369  // add to quest log
6370  if (slot < MAX_QUEST_LOG_SIZE && questStatusData.Status != QUEST_STATUS_NONE)
6371  {
6372  SetQuestSlot(slot, quest_id, uint32(quest_time)); // cast can't be helped
6373 
6374  if (questStatusData.Status == QUEST_STATUS_COMPLETE)
6375  SetQuestSlotState(slot, QUEST_STATE_COMPLETE);
6376  else if (questStatusData.Status == QUEST_STATUS_FAILED)
6377  SetQuestSlotState(slot, QUEST_STATE_FAIL);
6378 
6379  for (uint8 idx = 0; idx < QUEST_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; ++idx)
6380  if (questStatusData.CreatureOrGOCount[idx])
6381  SetQuestSlotCounter(slot, idx, questStatusData.CreatureOrGOCount[idx]);
6382 
6383  if (questStatusData.PlayerCount)
6384  SetQuestSlotCounter(slot, QUEST_PVP_KILL_SLOT, questStatusData.PlayerCount);
6385 
6386  ++slot;
6387  }
6388 
6389  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Quest status is {%u} for quest {%u} for player (%s)", questStatusData.Status, quest_id, GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
6390  }
6391  } while (result->NextRow());
6392  }
6393 
6394  // clear quest log tail
6395  for (uint16 i = slot; i < MAX_QUEST_LOG_SIZE; ++i)
6396  SetQuestSlot(i, 0);
6397 }

6399 void Player::_LoadQuestStatusRewarded(PreparedQueryResult result)
6400 {
6401  // SELECT quest FROM character_queststatus_rewarded WHERE guid = ?
6402 
6403  if (result)

6405  m_RewardedQuests.rehash(result->GetRowCount());

6409 
6410  uint32 quest_id = fields[0].GetUInt32();

6434 void Player::_LoadDailyQuestStatus(PreparedQueryResult result)
6435 {
6436  for (uint32 quest_daily_idx = 0; quest_daily_idx < PLAYER_MAX_DAILY_QUESTS; ++quest_daily_idx)
6437  SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_DAILY_QUESTS_1 + quest_daily_idx, 0);
6438 
6439  m_DFQuests.clear();
6440 
6441  //QueryResult* result = CharacterDatabase.PQuery("SELECT quest, time FROM character_queststatus_daily WHERE guid = '%u'", GetGUID().GetCounter());
6442 
6443  if (result)
6444  {
6445  uint32 quest_daily_idx = 0;
6446 
6447  do
6448  {
6449  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
6450  if (Quest const* qQuest = sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(fields[0].GetUInt32()))
6451  {
6452  if (qQuest->IsDFQuest())
6453  {
6454  m_DFQuests.insert(qQuest->GetQuestId());
6455  m_lastDailyQuestTime = time_t(fields[1].GetUInt32());
6456  continue;
6457  }
6458  }
6459 
6460  if (quest_daily_idx >= PLAYER_MAX_DAILY_QUESTS) // max amount with exist data in query
6461  {
6462  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player (%s) have more 25 daily quest records in `charcter_queststatus_daily`", GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
6463  break;
6464  }
6465 
6466  uint32 quest_id = fields[0].GetUInt32();
6467 
6468  // save _any_ from daily quest times (it must be after last reset anyway)
6469  m_lastDailyQuestTime = time_t(fields[1].GetUInt32());
6470 
6471  Quest const* quest = sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(quest_id);
6472  if (!quest)
6473  continue;
6474 
6475  SetUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_DAILY_QUESTS_1 + quest_daily_idx, quest_id);
6476  ++quest_daily_idx;
6477 
6478  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.loading", "Daily quest (%u) cooldown for player (%s)", quest_id, GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
6479  } while (result->NextRow());
6480  }
6481 
6482  m_DailyQuestChanged = false;
6483 }

6565 void Player::_LoadGroup()
6566 {
6567  if (uint32 groupId = GetGroupIdFromStorage(GetGUID().GetCounter()))
6568  if (Group* group = sGroupMgr->GetGroupByGUID(groupId))
6569  if (group->GetMemberGroup(GetGUID()) <= MAX_RAID_SUBGROUPS)
6570  {
6571  if (group->IsLeader(GetGUID()))
6572  SetFlag(PLAYER_FLAGS, PLAYER_FLAGS_GROUP_LEADER);
6573 
6574  uint8 subgroup = group->GetMemberGroup(GetGUID());
6575  SetGroup(group, subgroup);
6576 
6577  // the group leader may change the instance difficulty while the player is offline
6578  SetDungeonDifficulty(group->GetDungeonDifficulty());
6579  SetRaidDifficulty(group->GetRaidDifficulty());
6580  }
6581 
6582  if (!GetGroup() || !GetGroup()->IsLeader(GetGUID()))
6583  RemoveFlag(PLAYER_FLAGS, PLAYER_FLAGS_GROUP_LEADER);
6584 }

6598 void Player::SendRaidInfo()
6599 {
6600  uint32 counter = 0;
6601 
6602  WorldPacket data(SMSG_RAID_INSTANCE_INFO, 4);
6603 
6604  size_t p_counter = data.wpos();
6605  data << uint32(counter); // placeholder
6606 
6607  time_t now = time(nullptr);
6608 
6609  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_DIFFICULTY; ++i)
6610  {
6611  BoundInstancesMap const& m_boundInstances = sInstanceSaveMgr->PlayerGetBoundInstances(GetGUID(), Difficulty(i));
6612  for (BoundInstancesMap::const_iterator itr = m_boundInstances.begin(); itr != m_boundInstances.end(); ++itr)
6613  {
6614  if (itr->second.perm)
6615  {
6616  InstanceSave* save = itr->second.save;
6617  time_t resetTime = itr->second.extended ? save->GetExtendedResetTime() : save->GetResetTime();
6618  data << uint32(save->GetMapId()); // map id
6619  data << uint32(save->GetDifficulty()); // difficulty
6620  data << ObjectGuid::Create<HighGuid::Instance>(save->GetInstanceId()); // instance id
6621  data << uint8(1); // expired = 0
6622  data << uint8(itr->second.extended ? 1 : 0);// extended = 1
6623  data << uint32(resetTime >= now ? resetTime - now : 0); // reset time
6624  ++counter;
6625  }
6626  }
6627  }
6628  data.put<uint32>(p_counter, counter);
6629  GetSession()->SendPacket(&data);
6630 }

6632 /*
6633 - called on every successful teleportation to a map
6634 */
6635 void Player::SendSavedInstances()
6636 {
6637  bool hasBeenSaved = false;
6638  WorldPacket data;
6639 
6640  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_DIFFICULTY; ++i)
6641  {
6642  BoundInstancesMap const& m_boundInstances = sInstanceSaveMgr->PlayerGetBoundInstances(GetGUID(), Difficulty(i));
6643  for (BoundInstancesMap::const_iterator itr = m_boundInstances.begin(); itr != m_boundInstances.end(); ++itr)
6644  {
6645  if (itr->second.perm) // only permanent binds are sent
6646  {
6647  hasBeenSaved = true;
6648  break;
6649  }
6650  }
6651  }
6652 
6653  //Send opcode 811. true or false means, whether you have current raid/heroic instances
6654  data.Initialize(SMSG_UPDATE_INSTANCE_OWNERSHIP);
6655  data << uint32(hasBeenSaved);
6656  GetSession()->SendPacket(&data);
6657 
6658  if (!hasBeenSaved)
6659  return;
6660 
6661  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_DIFFICULTY; ++i)
6662  {
6663  BoundInstancesMap const& m_boundInstances = sInstanceSaveMgr->PlayerGetBoundInstances(GetGUID(), Difficulty(i));
6664  for (BoundInstancesMap::const_iterator itr = m_boundInstances.begin(); itr != m_boundInstances.end(); ++itr)
6665  {
6666  if (itr->second.perm)
6667  {
6668  data.Initialize(SMSG_UPDATE_LAST_INSTANCE);
6669  data << uint32(itr->second.save->GetMapId());
6670  GetSession()->SendPacket(&data);
6671  }
6672  }
6673  }
6674 }

6676 void Player::PrettyPrintRequirementsQuestList(const std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*>& missingQuests) const
6677 {
6678  LocaleConstant loc_idx = GetSession()->GetSessionDbLocaleIndex();
6679  for (const ProgressionRequirement* missingReq : missingQuests)
6680  {
6681  Quest const* questTemplate = sObjectMgr->GetQuestTemplate(missingReq->id);
6682  if (!questTemplate)
6683  {
6684  continue;
6685  }
6686 
6687  std::string questTitle = questTemplate->GetTitle();
6688  if (QuestLocale const* questLocale = sObjectMgr->GetQuestLocale(questTemplate->GetQuestId()))
6689  {
6690  ObjectMgr::GetLocaleString(questLocale->Title, loc_idx, questTitle);
6691  }
6692 
6693  std::stringstream stream;
6694  stream << "|cffff7c0a|Hquest:";
6695  stream << questTemplate->GetQuestId();
6696  stream << ":";
6697  stream << questTemplate->GetQuestLevel();
6698  stream << "|h[";
6699  stream << questTitle;
6700  stream << "]|h|r";
6701 
6702  if (missingReq->note.empty())
6703  {
6704  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(" - %s", stream.str().c_str());
6705  }
6706  else
6707  {
6708  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(" - %s %s %s", stream.str().c_str(), sObjectMgr->GetAcoreString(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_NOTE, loc_idx), missingReq->note.c_str());
6709  }
6710  }
6711 }

6784 bool Player::Satisfy(DungeonProgressionRequirements const* ar, uint32 target_map, bool report)
6785 {
6786  if (!IsGameMaster() && ar)
6787  {
6788  uint8 LevelMin = 0;
6789  uint8 LevelMax = 0;
6790 
6791  MapEntry const* mapEntry = sMapStore.LookupEntry(target_map);
6792  if (!mapEntry)
6793  return false;
6794 
6795  if (!sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_INSTANCE_IGNORE_LEVEL))
6796  {
6797  if (ar->levelMin && getLevel() < ar->levelMin)
6798  LevelMin = ar->levelMin;
6799  if (ar->levelMax && getLevel() > ar->levelMax)
6800  LevelMax = ar->levelMax;
6801  }
6802 
6803  if (DisableMgr::IsDisabledFor(DISABLE_TYPE_MAP, target_map, this))
6804  {
6805  GetSession()->SendAreaTriggerMessage("%s", GetSession()->GetAcoreString(LANG_INSTANCE_CLOSED));
6806  return false;
6807  }
6808 
6809  Player* partyLeader = this;
6810  std::string leaderName = m_session->GetAcoreString(LANG_YOU);
6811  {
6812  ObjectGuid leaderGuid = GetGroup() ? GetGroup()->GetLeaderGUID() : GetGUID();
6813  Player* tempLeader = HashMapHolder<Player>::Find(leaderGuid);
6814  if (leaderGuid != GetGUID())
6815  {
6816  if (tempLeader != nullptr)
6817  {
6818  partyLeader = tempLeader;
6819  }
6820  leaderName = GetGroup()->GetLeaderName();
6821  }
6822  }
6823 
6824  //Check all items
6825  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*> missingPlayerItems;
6826  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*> missingLeaderItems;
6827  for (const ProgressionRequirement* itemRequirement : ar->items)
6828  {
6829  Player* checkPlayer = this;
6830  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*>* missingItems = &missingPlayerItems;
6831  if (itemRequirement->checkLeaderOnly)
6832  {
6833  checkPlayer = partyLeader;
6834  missingItems = &missingLeaderItems;
6835  }
6836 
6837  if (itemRequirement->faction == TEAM_NEUTRAL || itemRequirement->faction == checkPlayer->GetTeamId(true))
6838  {
6839  if (!checkPlayer->HasItemCount(itemRequirement->id, 1))
6840  {
6841  missingItems->push_back(itemRequirement);
6842  }
6843  }
6844  }
6845 
6846  //Check all achievements
6847  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*> missingPlayerAchievements;
6848  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*> missingLeaderAchievements;
6849  for (const ProgressionRequirement* achievementRequirement : ar->achievements)
6850  {
6851  Player* checkPlayer = this;
6852  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*>* missingAchievements = &missingPlayerAchievements;
6853  if(achievementRequirement->checkLeaderOnly)
6854  {
6855  checkPlayer = partyLeader;
6856  missingAchievements = &missingLeaderAchievements;
6857  }
6858 
6859  if (achievementRequirement->faction == TEAM_NEUTRAL || achievementRequirement->faction == GetTeamId(true))
6860  {
6861  if (!checkPlayer || !checkPlayer->HasAchieved(achievementRequirement->id))
6862  {
6863  missingAchievements->push_back(achievementRequirement);
6864  }
6865  }
6866  }
6867 
6868  //Check all quests
6869  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*> missingPlayerQuests;
6870  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*> missingLeaderQuests;
6871  for (const ProgressionRequirement* questRequirement : ar->quests)
6872  {
6873  Player* checkPlayer = this;
6874  std::vector<const ProgressionRequirement*>* missingQuests = &missingPlayerQuests;
6875  if (questRequirement->checkLeaderOnly)
6876  {
6877  checkPlayer = partyLeader;
6878  missingQuests = &missingLeaderQuests;
6879  }
6880 
6881  if (questRequirement->faction == TEAM_NEUTRAL || questRequirement->faction == checkPlayer->GetTeamId(true))
6882  {
6883  if (!checkPlayer->GetQuestRewardStatus(questRequirement->id))
6884  {
6885  missingQuests->push_back(questRequirement);
6886  }
6887  }
6888  }
6889 
6890  //Check if avg ILVL requirement is allowed
6891  bool ilvlRequirementNotMet = false;
6892  if (sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_DUNGEON_ACCESS_REQUIREMENTS_PORTAL_CHECK_ILVL))
6893  {
6894  const int32 currentIlvl = (int32)GetAverageItemLevelForDF();
6895  if (ar->reqItemLevel > currentIlvl)
6896  {
6897  ilvlRequirementNotMet = true;
6898  }
6899  }
6900 
6901  Difficulty target_difficulty = GetDifficulty(mapEntry->IsRaid());
6902  MapDifficulty const* mapDiff = GetDownscaledMapDifficultyData(target_map, target_difficulty);
6903  if (LevelMin || LevelMax || ilvlRequirementNotMet
6904  || missingPlayerItems.size() || missingPlayerQuests.size() || missingPlayerAchievements.size()
6905  || missingLeaderItems.size() || missingLeaderQuests.size() || missingLeaderAchievements.size())
6906  {
6907  if (!sScriptMgr->NotAvoidSatisfy(partyLeader, ar, target_map, report))
6908  return true;
6909 
6910  if (report)
6911  {
6912  uint8 requirementPrintMode = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_DUNGEON_ACCESS_REQUIREMENTS_PRINT_MODE);
6913 
6914  if (requirementPrintMode == 0)
6915  {
6916  //Just print out the requirements are not met
6917  ChatHandler(GetSession()).SendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_NOT_MET);
6918  }
6919  else if(requirementPrintMode == 1)
6920  {
6921  //Blizzlike method of printing out the requirements
6922  if (missingLeaderQuests.size() && !missingLeaderQuests[0]->note.empty())
6923  {
6924  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage("%s", missingLeaderQuests[0]->note.c_str());
6925  }
6926  else if (mapDiff->hasErrorMessage)
6927  { // if (missingAchievement) covered by this case
6928  SendTransferAborted(target_map, TRANSFER_ABORT_DIFFICULTY, target_difficulty);
6929  }
6930  else if (missingPlayerItems.size())
6931  {
6932  GetSession()->SendAreaTriggerMessage(GetSession()->GetAcoreString(LANG_LEVEL_MINREQUIRED_AND_ITEM), LevelMin, sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(missingPlayerItems[0]->id)->Name1.c_str());
6933  }
6934  else if (LevelMin)
6935  {
6936  GetSession()->SendAreaTriggerMessage(GetSession()->GetAcoreString(LANG_LEVEL_MINREQUIRED), LevelMin);
6937  }
6938  else if (ilvlRequirementNotMet)
6939  {
6940  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_AVERAGE_ILVL_NOT_MET, ar->reqItemLevel, (uint16)GetAverageItemLevelForDF());
6941  }
6942  }
6943  else
6944  {
6945  bool errorAlreadyPrinted = false;
6946  //Pretty way of printing out requirements
6947  if (missingPlayerQuests.size())
6948  {
6949  ChatHandler(GetSession()).SendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_COMPLETE_QUESTS);
6950  PrettyPrintRequirementsQuestList(missingPlayerQuests);
6951  errorAlreadyPrinted = true;
6952  }
6953  if (missingLeaderQuests.size())
6954  {
6955  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_LEADER_COMPLETE_QUESTS, leaderName.c_str());
6956  PrettyPrintRequirementsQuestList(missingLeaderQuests);
6957  errorAlreadyPrinted = true;
6958  }
6959 
6960  if (missingPlayerAchievements.size())
6961  {
6962  ChatHandler(GetSession()).SendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_COMPLETE_ACHIEVEMENTS);
6963  PrettyPrintRequirementsAchievementsList(missingPlayerAchievements);
6964  errorAlreadyPrinted = true;
6965  }
6966  if (missingLeaderAchievements.size())
6967  {
6968  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_LEADER_COMPLETE_ACHIEVEMENTS, leaderName.c_str());
6969  PrettyPrintRequirementsAchievementsList(missingLeaderAchievements);
6970  errorAlreadyPrinted = true;
6971  }
6972 
6973  if (missingPlayerItems.size())
6974  {
6975  ChatHandler(GetSession()).SendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_OBTAIN_ITEMS);
6976  PrettyPrintRequirementsItemsList(missingPlayerItems);
6977  errorAlreadyPrinted = true;
6978  }
6979 
6980  if (missingLeaderItems.size())
6981  {
6982  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_LEADER_OBTAIN_ITEMS, leaderName.c_str());
6983  PrettyPrintRequirementsItemsList(missingLeaderItems);
6984  errorAlreadyPrinted = true;
6985  }
6986 
6987  if (ilvlRequirementNotMet)
6988  {
6989  ChatHandler(GetSession()).PSendSysMessage(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_AVERAGE_ILVL_NOT_MET, ar->reqItemLevel, (uint16)GetAverageItemLevelForDF());
6990  }
6991 
6992  if (LevelMin)
6993  {
6994  GetSession()->SendAreaTriggerMessage(GetSession()->GetAcoreString(LANG_LEVEL_MINREQUIRED), LevelMin);
6995  }
6996  else if (LevelMax)
6997  {
6998  GetSession()->SendAreaTriggerMessage(GetSession()->GetAcoreString(LANG_ACCESS_REQUIREMENT_MAX_LEVEL), LevelMax);
6999  }
7000  else if (mapDiff->hasErrorMessage && !errorAlreadyPrinted)
7001  {
7002  SendTransferAborted(target_map, TRANSFER_ABORT_DIFFICULTY, target_difficulty);
7003  }
7004  }
7005 
7006  //Print the extra string
7007  uint32 optionalStringID = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_DUNGEON_ACCESS_REQUIREMENTS_OPTIONAL_STRING_ID);
7008  if (optionalStringID > 0)
7009  {
7010  ChatHandler(GetSession()).SendSysMessage(optionalStringID);
7011  }
7012  }
7013  return false;
7014  }
7015  }
7016  return true;
7017 }

7019 bool Player::CheckInstanceLoginValid()
7020 {
7021  if (!GetMap())
7022  return false;
7023 
7024  if (!GetMap()->IsDungeon() || IsGameMaster())
7025  return true;
7026 
7027  if (GetMap()->IsRaid())
7028  {
7029  // cannot be in raid instance without a group
7030  if (!GetGroup())
7031  return false;
7032  }
7033  else
7034  {
7035  // cannot be in normal instance without a group and more players than 1 in instance
7036  if (!GetGroup() && GetMap()->GetPlayersCountExceptGMs() > 1)
7037  return false;
7038  }
7039 
7040  // pussywizard: check CanEnter for GetMap(), because in PlayerCannotEnter it is called for a map decided before loading screen (can change)
7041  if (GetMap()->CannotEnter(this, true))
7042  return false;
7043 
7044  // do checks for satisfy accessreqs, instance full, encounter in progress (raid), perm bind group != perm bind player
7045  return sMapMgr->PlayerCannotEnter(GetMap()->GetId(), this, true) == Map::CAN_ENTER;
7046 }

7048 bool Player::CheckInstanceCount(uint32 instanceId) const
7049 {
7050  if (_instanceResetTimes.size() < sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_MAX_INSTANCES_PER_HOUR))
7051  return true;
7052  return _instanceResetTimes.find(instanceId) != _instanceResetTimes.end();
7053 }

7055 bool Player::_LoadHomeBind(PreparedQueryResult result)
7056 {
7057  PlayerInfo const* info = sObjectMgr->GetPlayerInfo(getRace(true), getClass());
7058  if (!info)
7059  {
7060  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player (Name %s) has incorrect race/class pair. Can't be loaded.", GetName().c_str());
7061  return false;
7062  }
7063 
7064  bool ok = false;
7065  // SELECT mapId, zoneId, posX, posY, posZ FROM character_homebind WHERE guid = ?
7066  if (result)
7067  {
7068  Field* fields = result->Fetch();
7069 
7070  m_homebindMapId = fields[0].GetUInt16();
7071  m_homebindAreaId = fields[1].GetUInt16();
7072  m_homebindX = fields[2].GetFloat();
7073  m_homebindY = fields[3].GetFloat();
7074  m_homebindZ = fields[4].GetFloat();
7075 
7076  MapEntry const* bindMapEntry = sMapStore.LookupEntry(m_homebindMapId);
7077 
7078  // accept saved data only for valid position (and non instanceable), and accessable
7079  if (MapMgr::IsValidMapCoord(m_homebindMapId, m_homebindX, m_homebindY, m_homebindZ) &&
7080  !bindMapEntry->Instanceable() && GetSession()->Expansion() >= bindMapEntry->Expansion())
7081  ok = true;
7082  else
7083  {
7084  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_PLAYER_HOMEBIND);
7085  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7086  CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
7087  }
7088  }
7089 
7090  if (!ok)
7091  {
7092  m_homebindMapId = info->mapId;
7093  m_homebindAreaId = info->areaId;
7094  m_homebindX = info->positionX;
7095  m_homebindY = info->positionY;
7096  m_homebindZ = info->positionZ;
7097 
7098  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_PLAYER_HOMEBIND);
7099  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7100  stmt->setUInt16(1, m_homebindMapId);
7101  stmt->setUInt16(2, m_homebindAreaId);
7102  stmt->setFloat (3, m_homebindX);
7103  stmt->setFloat (4, m_homebindY);
7104  stmt->setFloat (5, m_homebindZ);
7105  CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
7106  }
7107 
7108  LOG_DEBUG("entities.player", "Setting player home position - mapid: %u, areaid: %u, X: %f, Y: %f, Z: %f",
7109  m_homebindMapId, m_homebindAreaId, m_homebindX, m_homebindY, m_homebindZ);
7110  return true;
7111 }

7126 void Player::SaveToDB(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans, bool create, bool logout)
7127 {
7128  // delay auto save at any saves (manual, in code, or autosave)
7129  m_nextSave = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_INTERVAL_SAVE);
7130 
7131  //lets allow only players in world to be saved
7132  if (IsBeingTeleportedFar())
7133  {
7134  ScheduleDelayedOperation(DELAYED_SAVE_PLAYER);
7135  return;
7136  }
7137 
7138  // pussywizard: full save now, so clear partial additional saves
7139  m_additionalSaveTimer = 0;
7140  m_additionalSaveMask = 0;
7141 
7142  // first save/honor gain after midnight will also update the player's honor fields
7143  UpdateHonorFields();
7144 
7145  LOG_DEBUG("entities.unit", "The value of player %s at save: ", m_name.c_str());
7146  outDebugValues();
7147 
7148  if (!create)
7149  sScriptMgr->OnPlayerSave(this);
7150 
7151  _SaveCharacter(create, trans);
7152 
7153  if (m_mailsUpdated) //save mails only when needed
7154  _SaveMail(trans);
7155 
7156  _SaveEntryPoint(trans);
7157  _SaveInventory(trans);
7158  _SaveQuestStatus(trans);
7159  _SaveDailyQuestStatus(trans);
7160  _SaveWeeklyQuestStatus(trans);
7161  _SaveSeasonalQuestStatus(trans);
7162  _SaveMonthlyQuestStatus(trans);
7163  _SaveTalents(trans);
7164  _SaveSpells(trans);
7165  _SaveSpellCooldowns(trans, logout);
7166  _SaveActions(trans);
7167  _SaveAuras(trans, logout);
7168  _SaveSkills(trans);
7169  m_achievementMgr->SaveToDB(trans);
7170  m_reputationMgr->SaveToDB(trans);
7171  _SaveEquipmentSets(trans);
7172  GetSession()->SaveTutorialsData(trans); // changed only while character in game
7173  _SaveGlyphs(trans);
7174  _SaveInstanceTimeRestrictions(trans);
7175 
7176  // check if stats should only be saved on logout
7177  // save stats can be out of transaction
7178  if (m_session->isLogingOut() || !sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_STATS_SAVE_ONLY_ON_LOGOUT))
7179  _SaveStats(trans);
7180 
7181  // save pet (hunter pet level and experience and all type pets health/mana).
7182  if (Pet* pet = GetPet())
7183  pet->SavePetToDB(PET_SAVE_AS_CURRENT, logout);
7184 
7185  // our: saving system
7186  if (!create && !logout)
7187  {
7188  // pussywizard: if it was not yet our time to save, be we are saved (additional save after important changes)
7189  // pussywizard: then free our original ticket in saving queue, so saving is fluent with no gaps
7190  SavingSystemMgr::InsertToSavingSkipListIfNeeded(m_nextSave);
7191 
7192  m_nextSave = SavingSystemMgr::IncreaseSavingMaxValue(1);
7193  }
7194 }

7211 void Player::_SaveActions(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)
7212 {
7213  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
7214 
7215  for (ActionButtonList::iterator itr = m_actionButtons.begin(); itr != m_actionButtons.end();)
7216  {
7217  switch (itr->second.uState)
7218  {
7219  case ACTIONBUTTON_NEW:
7220  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_ACTION);
7221  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7222  stmt->setUInt8(1, m_activeSpec);
7223  stmt->setUInt8(2, itr->first);
7224  stmt->setUInt32(3, itr->second.GetAction());
7225  stmt->setUInt8(4, uint8(itr->second.GetType()));
7226  trans->Append(stmt);
7227 
7228  itr->second.uState = ACTIONBUTTON_UNCHANGED;
7229  ++itr;
7230  break;
7231  case ACTIONBUTTON_CHANGED:
7232  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_CHAR_ACTION);
7233  stmt->setUInt32(0, itr->second.GetAction());
7234  stmt->setUInt8(1, uint8(itr->second.GetType()));
7235  stmt->setUInt32(2, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7236  stmt->setUInt8(3, itr->first);
7237  stmt->setUInt8(4, m_activeSpec);
7238  trans->Append(stmt);
7239 
7240  itr->second.uState = ACTIONBUTTON_UNCHANGED;
7241  ++itr;
7242  break;
7243  case ACTIONBUTTON_DELETED:
7244  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_ACTION_BY_BUTTON_SPEC);
7245  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7246  stmt->setUInt8(1, itr->first);
7247  stmt->setUInt8(2, m_activeSpec);
7248  trans->Append(stmt);
7249 
7250  m_actionButtons.erase(itr++);
7251  break;
7252  default:
7253  ++itr;
7254  break;
7255  }
7256  }
7257 }
7258 
7259 void Player::_SaveAuras(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans, bool logout)
7260 {
7261  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_AURA);
7262  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7263  trans->Append(stmt);
7264 
7265  for (AuraMap::const_iterator itr = m_ownedAuras.begin(); itr != m_ownedAuras.end(); ++itr)
7266  {
7267  if (!itr->second->CanBeSaved())
7268  continue;
7269 
7270  Aura* aura = itr->second;
7271  if( !logout && aura->GetDuration() < 60 * IN_MILLISECONDS )
7272  continue;
7273 
7274  int32 damage[MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS];
7275  int32 baseDamage[MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS];
7276  uint8 effMask = 0;
7277  uint8 recalculateMask = 0;
7278  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_EFFECTS; ++i)
7279  {
7280  if (AuraEffect const* effect = aura->GetEffect(i))
7281  {
7282  baseDamage[i] = effect->GetBaseAmount();
7283  damage[i] = effect->GetAmount();
7284  effMask |= 1 << i;
7285  if (effect->CanBeRecalculated())
7286  recalculateMask |= 1 << i;
7287  }
7288  else
7289  {
7290  baseDamage[i] = 0;
7291  damage[i] = 0;
7292  }
7293  }
7294 
7295  uint8 index = 0;
7296  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_AURA);
7297  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7298  stmt->setUInt64(index++, itr->second->GetCasterGUID().GetRawValue());
7299  stmt->setUInt64(index++, itr->second->GetCastItemGUID().GetRawValue());
7300  stmt->setUInt32(index++, itr->second->GetId());
7301  stmt->setUInt8(index++, effMask);
7302  stmt->setUInt8(index++, recalculateMask);
7303  stmt->setUInt8(index++, itr->second->GetStackAmount());
7304  stmt->setInt32(index++, damage[0]);
7305  stmt->setInt32(index++, damage[1]);
7306  stmt->setInt32(index++, damage[2]);
7307  stmt->setInt32(index++, baseDamage[0]);
7308  stmt->setInt32(index++, baseDamage[1]);
7309  stmt->setInt32(index++, baseDamage[2]);
7310  stmt->setInt32(index++, itr->second->GetMaxDuration());
7311  stmt->setInt32(index++, itr->second->GetDuration());
7312  stmt->setUInt8(index, itr->second->GetCharges());
7313  trans->Append(stmt);
7314  }
7315 }
7316 
7317 void Player::_SaveInventory(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)
7318 {
7319  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
7320  // force items in buyback slots to new state
7321  // and remove those that aren't already
7322  for (uint8 i = BUYBACK_SLOT_START; i < BUYBACK_SLOT_END; ++i)
7323  {
7324  Item* item = m_items[i];
7325  if (!item)
7326  continue;
7327 
7328  if (item->GetState() == ITEM_NEW)
7329  {
7330  // Xinef: item is removed, remove loot from storage if any
7331  if (item->GetTemplate()->Flags & ITEM_FLAG_HAS_LOOT)
7332  sLootItemStorage->RemoveStoredLoot(item->GetGUID());
7333  continue;
7334  }
7335 
7336  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_INVENTORY_BY_ITEM);
7337  stmt->setUInt32(0, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
7338  trans->Append(stmt);
7339 
7340  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_ITEM_INSTANCE);
7341  stmt->setUInt32(0, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
7342  trans->Append(stmt);
7343  m_items[i]->FSetState(ITEM_NEW);
7344 
7345  // Xinef: item is removed, remove loot from storage if any
7346  if (item->GetTemplate()->Flags & ITEM_FLAG_HAS_LOOT)
7347  sLootItemStorage->RemoveStoredLoot(item->GetGUID());
7348  }
7349 
7350  // Updated played time for refundable items. We don't do this in Player::Update because there's simply no need for it,
7351  // the client auto counts down in real time after having received the initial played time on the first
7352  // SMSG_ITEM_REFUND_INFO_RESPONSE packet.
7353  // Item::UpdatePlayedTime is only called when needed, which is in DB saves, and item refund info requests.
7354  RefundableItemsSet::iterator i_next;
7355  for (RefundableItemsSet::iterator itr = m_refundableItems.begin(); itr != m_refundableItems.end(); itr = i_next)
7356  {
7357  // use copy iterator because itr may be invalid after operations in this loop
7358  i_next = itr;
7359  ++i_next;
7360 
7361  Item* iPtr = GetItemByGuid((*itr));
7362  if (iPtr)
7363  {
7364  iPtr->UpdatePlayedTime(this);
7365  continue;
7366  }
7367  else
7368  {
7369  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Can't find item %s but is in refundable storage for player %s ! Removing.", (*itr).ToString().c_str(), GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
7370  m_refundableItems.erase(itr);
7371  }
7372  }
7373 
7374  // update enchantment durations
7375  for (EnchantDurationList::iterator itr = m_enchantDuration.begin(); itr != m_enchantDuration.end(); ++itr)
7376  itr->item->SetEnchantmentDuration(itr->slot, itr->leftduration, this);
7377 
7378  // if no changes
7379  if (m_itemUpdateQueue.empty())
7380  return;
7381 
7382  ObjectGuid::LowType lowGuid = GetGUID().GetCounter();
7383  for (size_t i = 0; i < m_itemUpdateQueue.size(); ++i)
7384  {
7385  Item* item = m_itemUpdateQueue[i];
7386  if (!item)
7387  continue;
7388 
7389  Bag* container = item->GetContainer();
7390  ObjectGuid::LowType bag_guid = container ? container->GetGUID().GetCounter() : 0;
7391 
7392  if (item->GetState() != ITEM_REMOVED)
7393  {
7394  Item* test = GetItemByPos(item->GetBagSlot(), item->GetSlot());
7395  if (test == nullptr)
7396  {
7397  ObjectGuid::LowType bagTestGUID = 0;
7398  if (Item* test2 = GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, item->GetBagSlot()))
7399  bagTestGUID = test2->GetGUID().GetCounter();
7400  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player(GUID: %u Name: %s)::_SaveInventory - the bag(%u) and slot(%u) values for the item %s (state %d) are incorrect, the player doesn't have an item at that position!",
7401  lowGuid, GetName().c_str(), item->GetBagSlot(), item->GetSlot(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), (int32)item->GetState());
7402  // according to the test that was just performed nothing should be in this slot, delete
7403  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_INVENTORY_BY_BAG_SLOT);
7404  stmt->setUInt32(0, bagTestGUID);
7405  stmt->setUInt8(1, item->GetSlot());
7406  stmt->setUInt32(2, lowGuid);
7407  trans->Append(stmt);
7408 
7409  RemoveTradeableItem(item); // pussywizard
7410  RemoveEnchantmentDurationsReferences(item); // pussywizard
7411  RemoveItemDurations(item); // pussywizard
7412 
7413  // also THIS item should be somewhere else, cheat attempt
7414  item->FSetState(ITEM_REMOVED); // we are IN updateQueue right now, can't use SetState which modifies the queue
7415  DeleteRefundReference(item->GetGUID());
7416  // don't skip, let the switch delete it
7417  continue;
7418  }
7419  else if (test != item)
7420  {
7421  LOG_ERROR("entities.player", "Player(GUID: %u Name: %s)::_SaveInventory - the bag(%u) and slot(%u) values for the item (%s) are incorrect, the item (%s) is there instead!",
7422  lowGuid, GetName().c_str(), item->GetBagSlot(), item->GetSlot(), item->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), test->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
7423  // save all changes to the item...
7424  if (item->GetState() != ITEM_NEW) // only for existing items, no dupes
7425  item->SaveToDB(trans);
7426  // ...but do not save position in invntory
7427  continue;
7428  }
7429  }
7430 
7431  switch (item->GetState())
7432  {
7433  case ITEM_NEW:
7434  case ITEM_CHANGED:
7435  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_REP_INVENTORY_ITEM);
7436  stmt->setUInt32(0, lowGuid);
7437  stmt->setUInt32(1, bag_guid);
7438  stmt->setUInt8 (2, item->GetSlot());
7439  stmt->setUInt32(3, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
7440  trans->Append(stmt);
7441  break;
7442  case ITEM_REMOVED:
7443  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_INVENTORY_BY_ITEM);
7444  stmt->setUInt32(0, item->GetGUID().GetCounter());
7445  trans->Append(stmt);
7446  case ITEM_UNCHANGED:
7447  break;
7448  }
7449 
7450  item->SaveToDB(trans); // item have unchanged inventory record and can be save standalone
7451  }
7452  m_itemUpdateQueue.clear();
7453 }

7455 void Player::_SaveMail(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)
7456 {
7457  if (!GetMailSize() || !m_mailsUpdated)
7458  {
7459  return;
7460  }
7461 
7462  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
7463 
7464  for (PlayerMails::iterator itr = m_mail.begin(); itr != m_mail.end(); ++itr)
7465  {
7466  Mail* m = (*itr);
7467  if (m->state == MAIL_STATE_CHANGED)
7468  {
7469  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_MAIL);
7470  stmt->setUInt8(0, uint8(m->HasItems() ? 1 : 0));
7471  stmt->setUInt32(1, uint32(m->expire_time));
7472  stmt->setUInt32(2, uint32(m->deliver_time));
7473  stmt->setUInt32(3, m->money);
7474  stmt->setUInt32(4, m->COD);
7475  stmt->setUInt8(5, uint8(m->checked));
7476  stmt->setUInt32(6, m->messageID);
7477 
7478  trans->Append(stmt);
7479 
7480  if (!m->removedItems.empty())
7481  {
7482  for (std::vector<uint32>::iterator itr2 = m->removedItems.begin(); itr2 != m->removedItems.end(); ++itr2)
7483  {
7484  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_MAIL_ITEM);
7485  stmt->setUInt32(0, *itr2);
7486  trans->Append(stmt);
7487  }
7488  m->removedItems.clear();
7489  }
7490  m->state = MAIL_STATE_UNCHANGED;
7491  }
7492  else if (m->state == MAIL_STATE_DELETED)
7493  {
7494  if (m->HasItems())
7495  {
7496  for (MailItemInfoVec::iterator itr2 = m->items.begin(); itr2 != m->items.end(); ++itr2)
7497  {
7498  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_ITEM_INSTANCE);
7499  stmt->setUInt32(0, itr2->item_guid);
7500  trans->Append(stmt);
7501  }
7502  }
7503  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_MAIL_BY_ID);
7504  stmt->setUInt32(0, m->messageID);
7505  trans->Append(stmt);
7506 
7507  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_MAIL_ITEM_BY_ID);
7508  stmt->setUInt32(0, m->messageID);
7509  trans->Append(stmt);
7510  }
7511  }
7512 
7513  //deallocate deleted mails...
7514  for (PlayerMails::iterator itr = m_mail.begin(); itr != m_mail.end();)
7515  {
7516  if ((*itr)->state == MAIL_STATE_DELETED)
7517  {
7518  Mail* m = *itr;
7519  m_mail.erase(itr);
7520  delete m;
7521  itr = m_mail.begin();
7522  }
7523  else
7524  ++itr;
7525  }
7526 
7527  m_mailsUpdated = false;
7528 }

7530 void Player::_SaveQuestStatus(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)
7531 {
7532  bool isTransaction = static_cast<bool>(trans);
7533  if (!isTransaction)
7534  trans = CharacterDatabase.BeginTransaction();
7535 
7536  QuestStatusSaveMap::iterator saveItr;
7537  QuestStatusMap::iterator statusItr;
7538  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
7539 
7540  bool keepAbandoned = !(sWorld->GetCleaningFlags() & CharacterDatabaseCleaner::CLEANING_FLAG_QUESTSTATUS);
7541 
7542  for (saveItr = m_QuestStatusSave.begin(); saveItr != m_QuestStatusSave.end(); ++saveItr)
7543  {
7544  if (saveItr->second)
7545  {
7546  statusItr = m_QuestStatus.find(saveItr->first);
7547  if (statusItr != m_QuestStatus.end() && (keepAbandoned || statusItr->second.Status != QUEST_STATUS_NONE))
7548  {
7549  uint8 index = 0;
7550  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_REP_CHAR_QUESTSTATUS);
7551 
7552  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7553  stmt->setUInt32(index++, statusItr->first);
7554  stmt->setUInt8(index++, uint8(statusItr->second.Status));
7555  stmt->setBool(index++, statusItr->second.Explored);
7556  stmt->setUInt32(index++, uint32(statusItr->second.Timer / IN_MILLISECONDS + sWorld->GetGameTime()));
7557 
7558  for (uint8 i = 0; i < QUEST_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; i++)
7559  stmt->setUInt16(index++, statusItr->second.CreatureOrGOCount[i]);
7560 
7561  for (uint8 i = 0; i < QUEST_ITEM_OBJECTIVES_COUNT; i++)
7562  stmt->setUInt16(index++, statusItr->second.ItemCount[i]);
7563 
7564  stmt->setUInt16(index, statusItr->second.PlayerCount);
7565  trans->Append(stmt);
7566  }
7567  }
7568  else
7569  {
7570  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_QUESTSTATUS_BY_QUEST);
7571  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7572  stmt->setUInt32(1, saveItr->first);
7573  trans->Append(stmt);
7574  }
7575  }
7576 
7577  m_QuestStatusSave.clear();
7578 
7579  for (saveItr = m_RewardedQuestsSave.begin(); saveItr != m_RewardedQuestsSave.end(); ++saveItr)
7580  {
7581  if (saveItr->second)
7582  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_QUESTSTATUS_REWARDED);
7583  else // xinef: what the fuck is this shit? quest can be removed by spelleffect if (!keepAbandoned)
7584  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_QUESTSTATUS_REWARDED_BY_QUEST);
7585 
7586  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7587  stmt->setUInt32(1, saveItr->first);
7588  trans->Append(stmt);
7589  }
7590 
7591  m_RewardedQuestsSave.clear();
7592 
7593  if (!isTransaction)
7594  CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
7595 }

7708 void Player::_SaveSkills(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)
7709 {
7710  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
7711  // we don't need transactions here.
7712  for (SkillStatusMap::iterator itr = mSkillStatus.begin(); itr != mSkillStatus.end();)
7713  {
7714  if (itr->second.uState == SKILL_UNCHANGED)
7715  {
7716  ++itr;
7717  continue;
7718  }
7719 
7720  if (itr->second.uState == SKILL_DELETED)
7721  {
7722  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_SKILL_BY_SKILL);
7723  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7724  stmt->setUInt32(1, itr->first);
7725  trans->Append(stmt);
7726 
7727  mSkillStatus.erase(itr++);
7728  continue;
7729  }
7730 
7731  uint32 valueData = GetUInt32Value(PLAYER_SKILL_VALUE_INDEX(itr->second.pos));
7732  uint16 value = SKILL_VALUE(valueData);
7733  uint16 max = SKILL_MAX(valueData);
7734 
7735  switch (itr->second.uState)
7736  {
7737  case SKILL_NEW:
7738  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_SKILLS);
7739  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7740  stmt->setUInt16(1, uint16(itr->first));
7741  stmt->setUInt16(2, value);
7742  stmt->setUInt16(3, max);
7743  trans->Append(stmt);
7744 
7745  break;
7746  case SKILL_CHANGED:
7747  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UDP_CHAR_SKILLS);
7748  stmt->setUInt16(0, value);
7749  stmt->setUInt16(1, max);
7750  stmt->setUInt32(2, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7751  stmt->setUInt16(3, uint16(itr->first));
7752  trans->Append(stmt);
7753 
7754  break;
7755  default:
7756  break;
7757  }
7758  itr->second.uState = SKILL_UNCHANGED;
7759 
7760  ++itr;
7761  }
7762 }

7764 void Player::_SaveSpells(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)
7765 {
7766  CharacterDatabasePreparedStatement* stmt = nullptr;
7767 
7768  for (PlayerSpellMap::iterator itr = m_spells.begin(); itr != m_spells.end();)
7769  {
7770  // xinef: skip temporary spells
7771  if (itr->second->State == PLAYERSPELL_TEMPORARY)
7772  {
7773  ++itr;
7774  continue;
7775  }
7776 
7777  // xinef: Delete statement for removed / updated spell
7778  if (itr->second->State == PLAYERSPELL_REMOVED || itr->second->State == PLAYERSPELL_CHANGED)
7779  {
7780  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_SPELL_BY_SPELL);
7781  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7782  stmt->setUInt32(1, itr->first);
7783  trans->Append(stmt);
7784  }
7785 
7786  // xinef: insert statement for new / updated spell
7787  if (itr->second->State == PLAYERSPELL_NEW || itr->second->State == PLAYERSPELL_CHANGED)
7788  {
7789  stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_SPELL);
7790  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7791  stmt->setUInt32(1, itr->first);
7792  stmt->setUInt8(2, itr->second->specMask);
7793  trans->Append(stmt);
7794  }
7795 
7796  if (itr->second->State == PLAYERSPELL_REMOVED)
7797  {
7798  delete itr->second;
7799  m_spells.erase(itr++);
7800  }
7801  else
7802  {
7803  itr->second->State = PLAYERSPELL_UNCHANGED;
7804  ++itr;
7805  }
7806  }

7811 void Player::_SaveStats(CharacterDatabaseTransaction trans)

7815  return;

7818

7820  stmt->setUInt32(0, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7821  trans->Append(stmt);
7822 
7823  uint8 index = 0;
7824

7826  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetGUID().GetCounter());
7827  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetMaxHealth());
7828 
7829  for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_POWERS; ++i)
7830  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetMaxPower(Powers(i)));
7831

7833  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetStat(Stats(i)));
7834

7836  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetResistance(SpellSchools(i)));

7840  stmt->setFloat(index++, GetFloatValue(PLAYER_PARRY_PERCENTAGE));
7841  stmt->setFloat(index++, GetFloatValue(PLAYER_CRIT_PERCENTAGE));
7842  stmt->setFloat(index++, GetFloatValue(PLAYER_RANGED_CRIT_PERCENTAGE));
7843  stmt->setFloat(index++, GetFloatValue(PLAYER_SPELL_CRIT_PERCENTAGE1));
7844  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetUInt32Value(UNIT_FIELD_ATTACK_POWER));
7845  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetUInt32Value(UNIT_FIELD_RANGED_ATTACK_POWER));
7846  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetBaseSpellPowerBonus());
7847  stmt->setUInt32(index++, GetUInt32Value(PLAYER_FIELD_COMBAT_RATING_1 + static_cast<uint16>(CR_CRIT_TAKEN_SPELL)));
7848 
7849  trans->Append(stmt);
7850 }
